------------------------------------------------
CHANGING BETWEEN MODES

i              - insert mode (inserting paths)
v              - visual mode (move around in 3D)
Esc            - default mode (edit paths)
:              - command mode

------------------------------------------------
COMMAND MODE

:h             - toggle this Help menu
:q             - quit
:w [filename]  - write to file, filename optional
:e [filename]  - edit file (i.e. open file)
:reset         - delete all paths
:pov           - generate and run povray file

:mv            - rename selected path
:ls            - change selected path line style
:rm            - remove selected path (delete)

------------------------------------------------
INSERT MODE

Mouse click    - place a path vertex
Mouse click x2 - ends the path
j              - move the insertion plane down
k              - move the insertion plane up
u              - undo last vertex placement
